Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:06.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}One after another, employees of a company called 'New Image' have been victims of assaults,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:10.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and the company president has been subject to threatening calls demanding money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:16.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And surprisingly, the criminal demanded that old man Mouri be the one to deliver the ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}M is heading south down Main Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The cruise with M on just passed Minato Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The suspect will pick up the money somewhere along the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Keep your eyes peeled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:39.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A transceiver has a range of 100 metres at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:42.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The criminal must be somewhere within that range!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's about time to get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The boat is about to pass the Ōshima River flood gates, and head into Ōyoko River.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}When it does, place the briefcase on the boat's roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Put it right in the middle so it doesn't fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Once that's done, sit down and await further instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}M has entered the Heikyū River.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The briefcase is on the boat's roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The briefcase is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:46.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The criminal fit the briefcase with electromagnets which were used to stick the briefcase to a steel bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:49.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and artfully steal away the 24 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:54.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We thought it suspicious that the criminal had requested the old man specifically, so we investigated,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and found one person who stood out:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:01.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Satoshi Nishizawa, a man who worked as a mechanic engineer for New Image.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:06.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The old man had identified him as a stalker as part of a job,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}which got him fired from New Image.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Looks like he's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ah, stop, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, you can't just\Nwalk into someone else's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:04.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It doesn't matter how many times you try,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:06.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}whether it's in love, deductions, today, or tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:07.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Can the case be solved with the suspect dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:10.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Where's the stolen money, and how will the case turn out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Wait, Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Even though the bath's full to the brim, there's no sign of any water that spilt out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It probably already dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}In other words, Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0} was placed in the bath quite some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Probably at least five or six hours have passed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Anyway, Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}, call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:43.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}An empty bottle of sleeping pills?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:45.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A flower petal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What kind of flower could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:51.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's shaped like a cherry blossom, but the colour's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, Ran-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Detective Satō! In the bathroom, Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}C-Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Takagi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, contact headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, Detective Satō, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}A stolen motorboat was found in Heikyū River.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We found fingerprints belonging to Satoshi Nishizawa on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, now that you know, leave it up to us. Out, out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well then, let's get out of here, so we don't get\Nin the way of their investigation, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, you can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}These are...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nishizawa committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:07:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}His fingerprints were found on a boat that we suspect was used to commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Also, this will was found on Nishizawa's PC.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The estimated time of death is around 1 AM today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He drowned after taking a large amount of sleeping pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}There's no doubt this was a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}'My goal was never the money.'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}'Kogorō Mouri, you took my pure love to be simply the\Nactions of a stalker, and turned me over to the police.'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}'On top of that, I was fired by President Ishida.'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}'My goals were to disgrace you, Great Detective,'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}'and punish President Ishida, who could\Nnot protect even one of his employees..'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}'I desire to continue this disgraced life no longer.'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}'I no longer have a reason to live.'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, we can't be sure without more evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's all we know for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Has the stolen money turned up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}See you later, Mouri-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You think you can call the case closed\Nwhen the money still hasn't been found?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}This case has yet to be solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I don't know anything about what happened to Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I heard you were on good terms with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Just tell me what you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\a6}Even if it's something you may rather not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:41.56,CharCards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,564)\fad(250,0)}Atsushi Tanaka (28)\NNew Image Engineer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I don't mind! Lemme hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0} held a grudge against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah, seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So, did he mention anything about his plans for the crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Do you have an alibi for 1 AM this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:01.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Why do I need an alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Wasn't it a suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That hasn't been settled yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, if we ask President Ishida's human relations\Ndepartment, the truth is bound to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If that's the case, then you should\Nbe doubting the president, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0} was extorting money from President Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's extortion, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:34.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Isn't it the president's job to look after his employees?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:38.03,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}How can you suggest that when you go hurting the company's image?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:40.41,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}If you're going to fire me, give me some proper compensation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.37,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now you're talking nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:45.04,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I'll tell everyone! I know you've been embezzling the company's money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.96,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I don't care if this company gets shut down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:52.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Don't lose your temper. Let's talk it over nice and slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The president had more than enough motive\Nfor murdering Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}, I'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So you're not going to tell me your alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I was at home talking with my girlfriend on the phone at 1 AM last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's not an alibi if it was a mobile, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It was a home phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If you doubt me, go check the call records or whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}There's no need to investigate, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Wasn't it a suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Don't you want to get the 24 million yen back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:25.50,CharCards,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(658,554)}Gen Ishida (42)\NNew Image President
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\a6}I don't care about such paltry sums.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\a6}I can get it back just by selling a few cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Thanks for your work. Now, please forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It must've been tough for you,\Nbeing chosen by Nishizawa and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Go on, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What is your alibi for 1 AM?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Me? I was asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I live alone, so there's nobody who can verify that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'll take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Aren't you going to take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Put it toward Nishizawa's funeral or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You should be doubting his subordinate, Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:11:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He was close to Nishizawa, liked to gamble,\Nand racked up quite large debts while doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He once came to me for help, but I refused, because he wanted more than I could reasonably advance him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A surveillance camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:20.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\blur7\3c&HCCFFFF}That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:24.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That's right, that road didn't have any surveillance cameras!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There aren't any cameras here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:34.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Whoops! Can't go straight ahead here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's the Toyosu Canal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:50.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There aren't any cameras on the route I just took, so if\Nsomeone came this way, they wouldn't have been recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So, they kept a boat moored here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:04.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}which they used to retrieve the briefcase left in Ōyoko River.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And this side canal here goes to the Sendai Canal area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Watch your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It seems narrow, but should be wide enough\Nfor a motorboat to fit through, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Aren't the cherry blossoms in full bloom great?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Stop over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}As I thought, this is where Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0} lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But I can't see any yellow flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, do you know a yellow flower that looks like a cherry blossom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, that must be a turmeric cherry blossom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Turmeric cherry blossom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Around here, you only see them in Tsukuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}They usually don't bloom until after the {\i1}Somei Yoshino{\i0} do,\Nbut for some reason they're already in bloom this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Let me see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:35.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What?! You've figured out the true culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I know who it is for sure, Inspector Megure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Didn't Nishizawa commit the crime, then kill himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's a wrong assumption!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Who is the true culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm keeping that a surprise for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Tell the president, Ishida-{\i1}san{\i0}, and the engineer,\NTanaka-{\i1}san{\i0} to go to the president's office at 5 PM today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, I can do that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Are you sure it's going to be okay, Mouri-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Have faith in the one and only Kogorō Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I told you not to go overworking yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Settle down and have some rest!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Understood, we'll be there right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Inspector, a large amount of ¥10,000 notes were reported\Nto be floating in Sumida River, in the vicinity of Tsukuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}This must the money from yesterday's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}They said they'd only found the empty briefcase, so the contents must've drifted away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:42.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The empty briefcase was found here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But we're over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:48.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Why isn't there any money floating in the river between the two places?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You can't keep going with this fever, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I've gotta perform the Great Detective\NKogorō Mouri's deduction show at five.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You really think a cold can keep me down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:15.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Tell him to stop, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Dad's insisting he performs a deduction show and won't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Did you figure out the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You'll have to wait and find out at five.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Now that you mention it, some of the\Nstolen money was found in Sumida River.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It looks like it had just been thrown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:34.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}This is bad. If the money's already been\Nfound, then my reasoning falls apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ah, my fever's taking over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's why I told you not to overwork yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}How about I do the performance instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We have a video camera, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So, it'd be fine if I record Uncle's deduction\Nand have everyone watch it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Uncle Kogorō couldn't come because of his cold,\Nso he told me to have you watch this recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's fine, just make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm a busy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}People all around the world know me as a Great Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's right! I—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:20.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}...am Kogorō Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}There are two keys to solving this case:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}A grudge held against New Image,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and someone who held a grudge towards me, Kogorō Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}There are three suspects:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Satoshi Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}, who died and left a will behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}His subordinate, Atsushi Tanaka-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And the president of New Image, Gen Ishida-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Satoshi Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0} harboured resentment towards both\Nthe Great Detective Kogorō Mouri and President Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Furthermore, he was blackmailing President Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}N-Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If you're gonna say Nishizawa was extorting me, then show me some evidence at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}President Ishida has no alibi for the time the money was taken at Ōyoko River,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}or for the time of Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}'s death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So he would be the most likely suspect if Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0} was murdered. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Even so, that doesn't mean I'm the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Tanaka-{\i1}san{\i0} had neither a grudge against\NNew Image, nor a reason to kill Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Furthermore, he {\i1}does{\i0} have an alibi for Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}'s estimated time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm glad he understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}However, because of Tanaka-{\i1}san{\i0}'s penchant for gambling, he had racked up huge debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}As such, he could've had a reason to commit the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But in the end, Tanaka-{\i1}san{\i0}'s innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}H-How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Taking into account the will left\Nbehind in Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}'s home,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}he must've fitted electromagnets inside the briefcase,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}stolen a motorboat and moored it in advance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and used them to steal the money at Ōyoko River.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Afterwards, he threw the case and the money in the river,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}returned home, took sleeping pills, and drowned in the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Therefore, Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0} committed suicide—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}W-What're you trying to say, Detective Mouri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Now, I'll finish Detective Mouri's deduction by reading this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Are you all right with that, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Detective Mouri says that the true culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Tanaka-{\i1}san{\i0}, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What's he saying?! I had an alibi, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You had debts of roughly 20 million yen\Nyou owed to banks from your gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You committed the crime in order to get the money to pay back your loans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Motive or no motive, how do you explain my alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'll explain it step by step.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}When he took the money, Tanaka-{\i1}san{\i0} didn't throw it away,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}instead just discarding the briefcase and the electromagnets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He then followed the canal and went to Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}'s home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You then knocked Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0} unconscious, put him on the boat and brought him back to your flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Your flat block is in Tsukuda, so you\Ncould take the waterway to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}In your flat, you made Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}\Ningest a large amount of sleeping pills,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:40.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and began preparing to make your murder look like a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:45.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You then called your girlfriend from your home phone, and at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}filled the bathtub with Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0} in with hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What I found suspicious was
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:58.32,Dialogue,,3,3,0,,{\blur1}that you happened to be talking to your girlfriend from your\Nhome phone at exactly Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}'s estimated time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It looked like an obvious attempt to create an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You also made a huge mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:16.34,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,{\blur1}You didn't realise that petal from the turmeric cherry\Nblossoms near your flat got stuck to Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}'s clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}After having created an alibi by being on the phone with your girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}you used the canal once again to return to Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}'s home,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and put his corpse in his own bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:33.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}In other words, you changed not the estimated time of death, but the location of the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}However, you failed to spot the turmeric cherry blossom petal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Your debts were 20 million yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and you initially intended to keep the entire 24 million yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}but since the crime had supposedly\Nbeen done only to carry out a grudge
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and then commit suicide after leaving a will behind on the computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:21:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}you were forced to throw the remaining four million yen into the river to support Nishizawa-{\i1}san{\i0}'s will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Is that so, Tanaka-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I-It's all a fabrication! A hoax!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I saw this mister riding a bike over Ōyoko River.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.82,0:21:18.86,FlashbackThoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur7}That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}A bike passed by me before the money was stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and then again after the theft had been carried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It had the same number plate as this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}This is your bike, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I found it parked in the company's parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You took a route without any\Nsurveillance cameras, but I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Damn it! And I thought you were a good person!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:22:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ishida-{\i1}san{\i0}, I'll be reporting your\Naccounting fraud to the Second Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You'd better be prepared for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}As I expect the Tax Office won't stay silent about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ah, that... is a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Can't you let it slip by just this once, detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, that's Mouri-{\i1}kun{\i0} for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Please let him know that he did a great\Njob even though he was sick, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.66,0:23:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.91,0:23:51.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Even though I had to re-edit the whole thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:19.31,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Take me to the high, we never cry on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:22.90,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}To a tomorrow we've never seen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:26.65,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Try again Try again Try again Always
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:29.95,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Try again Try again Try again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:33.03,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(0,300)}Speak out the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:42.75,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Not knowing exactly what you're searching for
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:46.21,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}living in the moment in your reckless way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:50.05,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}If you don't brighten up a bit soon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:53.35,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}you'll get crushed by your own anxiety
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:56.85,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Surely you have dreams too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:04:00.52,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I want to fulfill them, I want to cry... but I'll still chase them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:04.11,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Aren't you just quietly giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:08.19,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Can't you see now the reality you've distanced yourself from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:13.07,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Take me to the high, we never cry on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:16.49,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}To a tomorrow we've never seen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:20.08,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Try again Try again Try again Always
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:23.79,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Try again Try again Try again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:30.84,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Not everything is bad, we're dreamers after all
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:34.39,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Try again Try again Try again Always
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:38.14,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Try again Try again Try again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:41.52,OPTLTextless,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(0,500)}Speak out the truth!
